401
00:25:57,350 --> 00:25:57,940
My Lord.

402
00:25:58,590 --> 00:26:00,460
He's targeting you.

403
00:26:00,480 --> 00:26:01,090
My Lord.

404
00:26:09,400 --> 00:26:09,980
My Lord.

405
00:26:11,270 --> 00:26:11,830
My Lord.

