420
00:26:52,000 --> 00:26:53,730
Take Chu Huaiming to the Court of Judicial Review.

421
00:26:54,070 --> 00:26:54,380
Get up.

422
00:26:54,550 --> 00:26:55,090
My Lord.

423
00:26:55,750 --> 00:26:56,490
Zang Hai.

424
00:26:57,000 --> 00:26:58,490
I hope you die!

425
00:26:59,270 --> 00:27:00,700
I hope you die!

426
00:27:01,920 --> 00:27:03,460
Go get water.

427
00:27:04,000 --> 00:27:05,090
Hurry.

428
00:27:06,000 --> 00:27:06,660
Hurry.

429
00:27:08,720 --> 00:27:09,380
Faster.

430
00:27:17,310 --> 00:27:18,460
You mean

431
00:27:18,790 --> 00:27:21,940
our Lord dashed into the fire

432
00:27:22,070 --> 00:27:23,140
to save Zang Hai?

433
00:27:24,550 --> 00:27:26,730
Fortunately, the arsonist was caught.

434
00:27:28,000 --> 00:27:28,700
Who was it?

435
00:27:29,270 --> 00:27:29,940
Chu Huaiming.

436
00:27:32,830 --> 00:27:34,620
The second young master caught him

437
00:27:35,440 --> 00:27:38,010
and he's escorting him to the Court of Judicial Review now.

438
00:27:39,920 --> 00:27:40,660
Zhifu, hurry up.

439
00:27:41,240 --> 00:27:42,010
Let's check on him.

440
00:27:42,070 --> 00:27:42,460
Alright.

441
00:27:43,310 --> 00:27:44,770
Don't worry, My Lady.

442
00:27:45,110 --> 00:27:47,900
Mr. Zang has sent our Lord back to his chamber for treatment.

443
00:27:48,510 --> 00:27:52,220
Our Lord said that you and Young Master were not needed there.

444
00:28:09,070 --> 00:28:09,490
Zhifu.

445
00:28:12,750 --> 00:28:14,420
Someone beat us to it.

446
00:28:15,830 --> 00:28:17,900
You are supposed to be the one

447
00:28:19,240 --> 00:28:20,380
staying by your father's side now.

448
00:28:29,510 --> 00:28:30,010
My Lord.

449
00:28:30,640 --> 00:28:31,620
The physicians will be here soon.

450
00:28:32,750 --> 00:28:34,860
No need to make a fuss over some minor injuries.

451
00:28:35,160 --> 00:28:36,770
We'll be done before they arrive.

452
00:28:38,070 --> 00:28:38,530
Go on.

453
00:28:42,240 --> 00:28:43,530
Please bear with it, My Lord.

454
00:28:49,350 --> 00:28:50,460
As you said,

455
00:28:51,550 --> 00:28:52,570
General Fu died.

456
00:28:53,240 --> 00:28:55,380
The Great Yong lost an outstanding general.

457
00:28:56,680 --> 00:28:57,420
To be honest,

458
00:28:59,000 --> 00:29:01,860
I am somewhat relieved.

459
00:29:05,110 --> 00:29:06,490
I've been wondering

460
00:29:07,920 --> 00:29:09,770
whether the falling star would be me.

461
00:29:12,510 --> 00:29:13,330
You are over-concerned.

462
00:29:14,160 --> 00:29:15,490
I have told you

463
00:29:16,270 --> 00:29:16,770
that you

464
00:29:17,440 --> 00:29:18,530
