466
00:29:22,720 --> 00:29:23,660
fearless of death.

467
00:29:24,550 --> 00:29:25,900
But life in the capital

468
00:29:27,350 --> 00:29:29,050
has changed me over time.

469
00:29:34,310 --> 00:29:35,730
Fortunately, I have you

470
00:29:36,830 --> 00:29:38,980
to take precautions for me.

471
00:29:57,270 --> 00:29:57,770
My Lord.

472
00:29:59,270 --> 00:30:00,420
