477
00:30:11,400 --> 00:30:11,810
Zang Hai.

478
00:30:13,200 --> 00:30:16,250
I used to think of you as an aide.

479
00:30:16,830 --> 00:30:19,050
You were my subordinate, nothing more.

480
00:30:20,920 --> 00:30:23,570
But after I rescued you from the fire, I realized

481
00:30:24,590 --> 00:30:27,490
that I have long regarded you as my family.

482
00:30:29,640 --> 00:30:32,180
I locked you up out of concern.

483
00:30:32,510 --> 00:30:33,010
Don't blame me.

484
00:30:35,720 --> 00:30:36,380
I dare not.

485
00:30:37,160 --> 00:30:38,700
I overstepped my authority...

486
00:30:38,830 --> 00:30:39,530
Enough.

487
00:30:40,310 --> 00:30:41,700
I know you meant well.

488
00:30:42,510 --> 00:30:43,220
I understand

489
00:30:44,240 --> 00:30:45,140
what you said.

490
00:30:49,720 --> 00:30:52,660
It's hard for me to trust someone.

491
00:30:54,510 --> 00:30:55,330
Don't let me down.

492
00:30:58,680 --> 00:30:59,250
I swear

493
00:31:00,070 --> 00:31:01,420
I will never let you down.

494
00:31:10,540 --> 00:31:11,400
[The Great Prison]

495
00:31:11,400 --> 00:31:14,660
By the Mandate of Heaven, His Majesty decrees:

496
00:31:15,000 --> 00:31:17,980
Chu Huaiming, Imperial Astronomer of the Imperial Astronomical Bureau,

497
00:31:18,200 --> 00:31:21,010
misread celestial omens and delayed warnings,

498
00:31:21,550 --> 00:31:24,730
which led to great floods in Zhongzhou that ruined people's livelihood.

499
00:31:25,110 --> 00:31:28,010
Then he hid the truth from his superiors and plotted to kill the innocent.

500
00:31:28,590 --> 00:31:31,860
He is hereby stripped of rank, reduced to common status,

501
00:31:32,270 --> 00:31:34,050
and exiled to a distance of 3000 li

502
00:31:34,510 --> 00:31:38,660
with 50 strokes of the rod to be carried out right now.

503
00:31:52,590 --> 00:31:53,090
My Lady,

504
00:31:53,550 --> 00:31:54,530
did I hurt you?

505
00:31:56,400 --> 00:31:57,460
It's not your fault.

506
00:31:59,920 --> 00:32:00,810
I have a headache.

507
00:32:03,240 --> 00:32:04,380
What is on your mind?

508
00:32:04,880 --> 00:32:07,010
Are you still worried about our Lord's injury?

509
00:32:08,070 --> 00:32:09,050
Mr. Zhuang said

510
00:32:09,510 --> 00:32:11,860
that our Lord is going to be alright.

511
00:32:14,790 --> 00:32:15,900
I was thinking

512
00:32:17,550 --> 00:32:20,660
about Zang Hai and Zhuang Zhixing.

513
00:32:22,480 --> 00:32:25,620
Why would you think about them?

514
00:32:26,110 --> 00:32:27,530
Don't let them bother you.

515
00:32:30,400 --> 00:32:33,330
Zhixing did well in the ground polo match,

516
00:32:34,480 --> 00:32:35,860
which pleased his father.

517
00:32:37,270 --> 00:32:40,010
While Zhifu chose scholarship, he turned to martial arts.

518
00:32:40,880 --> 00:32:42,940
He knew very well that our Lord craved

519
00:32:43,640 --> 00:32:45,810
a martial heir to carry on the legacy

520
00:32:46,440 --> 00:32:48,770
and bring the Zhuang family back to glory.

521
00:32:49,830 --> 00:32:51,940
And he just happened

522
00:32:53,440 --> 00:32:55,620
to catch Chu Huaiming who set fire.

523
00:32:56,830 --> 00:32:58,180
He earned merit, and meanwhile,

524
00:32:59,110 --> 00:33:00,220
helped Zang Hai.

525
00:33:03,510 --> 00:33:07,140
What an accurate plan refined down

526
00:33:08,880 --> 00:33:10,140
to the last detail.

527
00:33:11,480 --> 00:33:14,980
Did the second young master suddenly get enlightened?

528
00:33:16,110 --> 00:33:17,090
I'm worried

529
00:33:19,070 --> 00:33:20,530
that he has allied with Zang Hai to...

530
00:33:30,510 --> 00:33:31,570
Although

531
00:33:32,880 --> 00:33:35,050
I don't know what Zang Hai is after,

532
00:33:36,480 --> 00:33:37,620
I'm sure

533
00:33:39,270 --> 00:33:42,250
that Zhixing is trying to compete with Zhifu.

534
00:33:43,030 --> 00:33:44,530
There's nothing to be afraid of.

535
00:33:45,350 --> 00:33:46,330
That good-for-nothing

536
00:33:47,350 --> 00:33:49,860
is no match for our young master.

537
00:34:06,070 --> 00:34:06,980
I made

538
00:34:07,270 --> 00:34:09,090
this ginseng soup for you by myself.

539
00:34:09,670 --> 00:34:11,570
It has cinnamon and licorice

540
00:34:12,230 --> 00:34:13,340
that drain pus.

541
00:34:14,070 --> 00:34:16,740
Have some and your wounds will heal faster.

542
00:34:19,320 --> 00:34:20,610
How are you feeling?

543
00:34:21,280 --> 00:34:22,380
Does it still hurt?

544
00:34:23,550 --> 00:34:25,380
You didn't let me take care of you.

545
00:34:25,960 --> 00:34:27,490
I've been worried all night.

546
00:34:28,670 --> 00:34:31,210
It's just a minor injury. No big deal.

547
00:34:32,000 --> 00:34:32,830
Your safety

548
00:34:32,830 --> 00:34:35,570
concerns the livelihoods of hundreds of people in this household.

549
00:34:36,280 --> 00:34:37,650
How can I not be concerned?

550
00:34:38,480 --> 00:34:39,690
Please don't put yourself

551
00:34:40,150 --> 00:34:41,980
