554
00:34:59,590 --> 00:35:00,820
But for some reason,

555
00:35:01,880 --> 00:35:04,740
I've been quite uneasy.

556
00:35:07,670 --> 00:35:08,980
What are you worried about?

557
00:35:10,510 --> 00:35:12,010
Ever since Zang Hai came,

558
00:35:12,630 --> 00:35:14,980
