559
00:35:15,590 --> 00:35:17,210
Yang Zhen and Qu Jiao died.

560
00:35:18,360 --> 00:35:20,860
Now, even Chu Huaiming is in jail.

561
00:35:21,550 --> 00:35:23,940
Think about it, My Lord.

562
00:35:25,000 --> 00:35:26,610
Who benefits the most from it?

563
00:35:28,670 --> 00:35:30,340
Isn't it Zang Hai?

564
00:35:32,280 --> 00:35:33,490
You treat him so well.

565
00:35:34,070 --> 00:35:37,420
How come he keeps eliminating dissidents?

566
00:35:38,550 --> 00:35:39,460
Eliminating dissidents?

567
00:35:41,510 --> 00:35:41,980
My love.

568
00:35:42,710 --> 00:35:43,650
