569
00:35:44,030 --> 00:35:45,170
Zang Hai came

570
00:35:45,590 --> 00:35:47,300
and instantly bonded with Zhixing.

571
00:35:47,960 --> 00:35:51,130
I'm afraid it was because Zhixing was simple

572
00:35:51,360 --> 00:35:52,690
and liked to make friends.

573
00:35:53,510 --> 00:35:54,420
Yesterday,

574
00:35:54,630 --> 00:35:56,900
Zhixing happened to catch Chu Huaiming.

575
00:35:58,230 --> 00:36:00,820
What a coincidence.

576
00:36:07,030 --> 00:36:07,980
Are you saying

577
00:36:09,630 --> 00:36:12,300
that Zhixing knew Chu Huaiming would set fire

578
00:36:13,000 --> 00:36:14,010
and lay in ambush?

579
00:36:14,590 --> 00:36:15,490
I'm afraid

580
00:36:16,360 --> 00:36:17,820
that someone has been guiding him.

581
00:36:18,360 --> 00:36:20,180
Otherwise, how did he win the ground polo game

582
00:36:20,280 --> 00:36:21,530
just like that?

583
00:36:22,320 --> 00:36:22,780
My love.

584
00:36:24,150 --> 00:36:25,340
I know you want Zhifu to do well.

585
00:36:26,110 --> 00:36:27,570
But as the female head of the household,

586
00:36:28,230 --> 00:36:30,260
how come you won't accept Zhixing's success?

587
00:36:37,710 --> 00:36:39,420
You got me wrong, My Lord.

588
00:36:42,230 --> 00:36:43,690
I'm just worried

589
00:36:44,280 --> 00:36:46,380
that your trusted and well-respected aide

590
00:36:47,110 --> 00:36:47,980
is actually

591
00:36:49,230 --> 00:36:51,050
harboring other intentions.

592
00:36:54,960 --> 00:36:55,980
I heard

593
00:36:57,760 --> 00:36:58,650
what you said.

594
00:36:59,440 --> 00:37:00,210
You may leave.

595
00:37:13,710 --> 00:37:14,090
My Lady.

596
00:37:30,880 --> 00:37:31,300
My Lord.

597
00:37:32,960 --> 00:37:34,820
You heard everything?

598
00:37:35,840 --> 00:37:36,380
My Lord.

599
00:37:36,960 --> 00:37:38,570
Yes, I heard everything.

600
00:37:39,710 --> 00:37:40,690
Have anything to say?

601
00:37:43,760 --> 00:37:46,130
My Lady is only partly right.

602
00:37:48,360 --> 00:37:49,940
I did train the second young master

603
00:37:50,480 --> 00:37:51,650
to win the game.

604
00:37:52,110 --> 00:37:53,420
But how could I have known

605
00:37:53,710 --> 00:37:55,860
that Chu Huaiming would come to set fire?

606
00:37:57,440 --> 00:37:58,300
Everyone rushed

607
00:37:58,710 --> 00:38:00,740
to the confinement chamber to put out the fire.

608
00:38:01,630 --> 00:38:03,820
Chu Huaiming must have looked suspicious

609
00:38:04,280 --> 00:38:05,210
as he fled in panic.

610
00:38:06,150 --> 00:38:07,380
Young Master spotted him.

611
00:38:07,710 --> 00:38:08,780
The arrest was only natural.

612
00:38:10,070 --> 00:38:11,690
But I admit

613
00:38:12,880 --> 00:38:15,130
that I have been close to the second young master.

614
00:38:16,630 --> 00:38:17,090
My Lord.

615
00:38:17,960 --> 00:38:19,570
If I may be so bold,

616
00:38:20,400 --> 00:38:22,420
the second young master can be a great general.

617
00:38:23,550 --> 00:38:25,460
He can't fully unleash his potential

618
00:38:26,400 --> 00:38:27,300
by playing ground polo.

619
00:38:30,070 --> 00:38:31,090
Are you saying

620
00:38:31,960 --> 00:38:33,530
that I should put him in the army?

621
00:38:35,280 --> 00:38:35,690
That's right.

622
00:38:37,000 --> 00:38:38,530
Your outstanding elder son

623
00:38:39,230 --> 00:38:40,980
has established himself in the imperial court.

624
00:38:41,670 --> 00:38:43,980
But your family boasts generations of generals

625
00:38:44,360 --> 00:38:46,300
and you have made great achievements yourself.

626
00:38:47,030 --> 00:38:48,050
It would be a pity

627
00:38:48,760 --> 00:38:51,460
if the legacy finds no bearer.

628
00:38:58,510 --> 00:39:01,980
Zhifu is not made for the army for sure.

629
00:39:04,070 --> 00:39:04,980
But I'm afraid

630
00:39:06,840 --> 00:39:08,210
that you are wrong about Zhixing.

631
00:39:10,800 --> 00:39:13,130
He may have been a bit wayward in the past

632
00:39:13,760 --> 00:39:14,740
but he's been

633
00:39:15,110 --> 00:39:17,340
practicing hard without slacking off these days.

634
00:39:18,360 --> 00:39:20,940
The reason he could stand out so fast,

635
00:39:21,590 --> 00:39:22,740
apart from his diligence,

636
00:39:23,440 --> 00:39:26,010
lay in the blood of the Zhuang family

637
00:39:26,190 --> 00:39:27,900
flowing through his veins.

638
00:39:28,480 --> 00:39:31,340
Isn't it a bit too early to make plans

639
00:39:33,320 --> 00:39:34,340
for Zhixing?

640
00:39:35,230 --> 00:39:36,980
As your aide,

641
00:39:37,670 --> 00:39:39,650
of course, I have to make plans for your family.

642
00:39:40,590 --> 00:39:42,130
Once we have a scholar

643
00:39:42,440 --> 00:39:44,820
and a general supporting each other in court,

644
00:39:45,510 --> 00:39:48,090
we can lay a solid foundation for further development.

645
00:39:49,800 --> 00:39:50,860
You perceive

646
00:39:51,360 --> 00:39:52,460
and contemplate things

647
00:39:53,670 --> 00:39:54,780
far beyond my capacity.

648
00:39:56,670 --> 00:39:57,940
My Lord, you said

649
00:39:58,550 --> 00:39:59,780
you'd treat me as family.

650
00:40:00,480 --> 00:40:02,650
Then I shall share everything on my mind

651
00:40:03,230 --> 00:40:04,420
without holding back.

652
00:40:07,110 --> 00:40:09,860
Back then, aides like you around me

653
00:40:10,710 --> 00:40:12,570
couldn't even fit in one tent.

654
00:40:13,880 --> 00:40:14,940
But they are all dead.

655
00:40:16,670 --> 00:40:17,740
They died for me.

656
00:40:22,230 --> 00:40:23,090
Are you afraid of death?

657
00:40:25,920 --> 00:40:26,490
My Lord.

658
00:40:27,510 --> 00:40:30,010
I once said that I was afraid of death.

659
00:40:30,960 --> 00:40:32,380
But it's worse to live a wasted life.

660
00:40:33,440 --> 00:40:35,050
I believe those who worked for you

661
00:40:36,070 --> 00:40:37,380
died for a great cause.

662
00:40:42,710 --> 00:40:44,690
I called you here to talk business.

663
00:40:48,630 --> 00:40:51,050
The Imperial Astronomer post is vacant.

664
00:40:52,190 --> 00:40:52,740
Tell me.

665
00:40:54,030 --> 00:40:56,300
Do you want to take that job?

666
00:40:59,230 --> 00:41:00,090
I...

667
00:41:00,150 --> 00:41:00,900
Don't hesitate.

668
00:41:01,590 --> 00:41:03,940
If you're interested, I will pull some strings for you.

669
00:41:07,590 --> 00:41:08,650
I will do whatever you say.

670
00:41:11,460 --> 00:41:13,580
[Sangu Bookshop]

671
00:41:14,070 --> 00:41:16,940
Hai, you were really lucky this time.

672
00:41:17,920 --> 00:41:19,050
How much of his trust

673
00:41:19,150 --> 00:41:21,210
do you think you've earned by now?

674
00:41:23,800 --> 00:41:24,570
About 70 or 80 percent.

675
00:41:28,070 --> 00:41:29,090
You disagree, Master?

676
00:41:29,710 --> 00:41:32,380
If the person caught in the fire was not you but Jiang Xiang,

677
00:41:33,150 --> 00:41:34,690
he wouldn't have saved her.

678
00:41:35,880 --> 00:41:36,980
Jiang Xiang's father Jiang Jin

679
00:41:37,000 --> 00:41:38,980
is no longer the Minister of Rites

680
00:41:39,510 --> 00:41:40,860
and has no value to the Marquis.

681
00:41:42,070 --> 00:41:45,130
But you are his most precious aide now.

682
00:41:46,110 --> 00:41:47,340
Your talents and abilities

683
00:41:47,630 --> 00:41:50,130
can help him stand firm in the court.

684
00:41:50,840 --> 00:41:51,490
He saved you

685
00:41:51,960 --> 00:41:53,820
to protect his private property.

686
00:41:54,360 --> 00:41:56,300
He said what he said

687
00:41:57,150 --> 00:41:58,780
just to win your heart.

688
00:41:59,280 --> 00:42:00,460
At least, it is good

689
00:42:00,630 --> 00:42:03,900
that the Marquis of Pingjin is trying to bond with you.

690
00:42:04,710 --> 00:42:06,340
But you must be extra careful.

691
00:42:07,110 --> 00:42:08,090
Never cross the line

692
00:42:08,360 --> 00:42:09,740
or fail to show due respect.

693
00:42:10,150 --> 00:42:11,780
This is quite tricky.

694
00:42:13,230 --> 00:42:14,260
I hope you can be the person

695
00:42:14,280 --> 00:42:16,740
he trusts and depends on the most.

696
00:42:17,480 --> 00:42:20,210
Then he will share everything on his mind with you.

697
00:42:21,320 --> 00:42:22,820
We are not bound by blood.

698
00:42:23,000 --> 00:42:24,610
I can earn his trust,

699
00:42:25,230 --> 00:42:26,690
but how can I make him rely on me

700
00:42:27,510 --> 00:42:29,210
without working for him

701
00:42:29,320 --> 00:42:30,340
a decade?

702
00:42:31,670 --> 00:42:32,820
Not even Yang Zhen made it.

703
00:42:34,920 --> 00:42:36,690
Everyone experiences pain and confusion.

704
00:42:37,030 --> 00:42:37,980
It's hard to take action.

705
00:42:38,630 --> 00:42:39,650
The Marquis is no exception.

706
00:42:41,280 --> 00:42:43,490
To make him rely on you,

707
00:42:44,110 --> 00:42:46,010
you must share his burden.

708
00:42:47,030 --> 00:42:49,210
What pains and confuses him?

709
00:42:51,360 --> 00:42:54,340
It concerns the person who disappeared from the Zhuang family.

710
00:43:22,260 --> 00:43:26,940
♪Conceal the ambition in my eyes♪

711
00:43:29,460 --> 00:43:36,100
♪In my palm, I hold a dangerous desire♪

712
00:43:36,660 --> 00:43:39,420
♪Turbulent waves hidden in my sleeves♪

713
00:43:40,020 --> 00:43:42,740
♪Silent thunder echoes around♪

714
00:43:43,020 --> 00:43:44,980
♪However cunning you are♪

715
00:43:45,460 --> 00:43:47,540
♪I can see♪

716
00:43:49,260 --> 00:43:51,380
♪Right through you♪

717
00:43:57,740 --> 00:44:04,780
♪Schemes are my armor♪

718
00:44:04,940 --> 00:44:10,380
♪Overt plans are my weapons♪

719
00:44:11,940 --> 00:44:14,660
♪With restrained fury♪

720
00:44:15,340 --> 00:44:18,020
♪I purge the world's corruption♪

721
00:44:18,220 --> 00:44:20,260
♪The night is not dark♪

722
00:44:20,740 --> 00:44:22,820
♪Because♪

723
00:44:23,940 --> 00:44:29,420
♪My heart burns bright♪

724
00:44:32,220 --> 00:44:35,500
♪I control the shifting clouds♪

725
00:44:35,700 --> 00:44:38,260
♪I command the falling rain♪

726
00:44:38,420 --> 00:44:40,780
♪The compass of the human soul is unpredictable♪

727
00:44:40,900 --> 00:44:45,700
♪There will always be ups and downs♪

728
00:44:46,180 --> 00:44:49,500
♪I hold the power of life and death♪

729
00:44:49,700 --> 00:44:52,260
♪I grant and I take away♪

730
00:44:52,420 --> 00:44:55,940
♪When faith burns like the scorching sun♪

731
00:44:55,980 --> 00:44:59,460
♪I will sing aloud with you♪

732
00:44:59,580 --> 00:45:02,820
♪I am the sowing season♪

733
00:45:02,940 --> 00:45:06,220
♪I am the autumn harvest♪

734
00:45:06,460 --> 00:45:08,620
♪I am the world♪

735
00:45:08,820 --> 00:45:12,380
♪I am the people♪

736
00:45:13,580 --> 00:45:16,660
♪And you are also me♪
